WEBVTT

00:01.150 --> 00:05.450
In hindsight, we accomplished what was required. 

00:06.500 --> 00:08.800
With Unicron's awakening,

00:09.020 --> 00:10.020
extreme measures needed to be taken.

00:11.530 --> 00:13.630
Enemies became allies,

00:13.680 --> 00:15.780
allies became confidants.

00:17.330 --> 00:18.830
And, with the Matrix of Leadership,

00:21.120 --> 00:23.220
the planet Earth was saved.

00:25.450 --> 00:28.250
Though at immeasurable personal cost...

00:28.320 --> 00:30.620
When Optimus surrendered the Matrix

00:30.690 --> 00:33.890
he'd lost more than the collective
wisdom of the Primes.

00:33.990 --> 00:35.190
Who are they?

00:35.470 --> 00:36.470
Our mortal enemies!

00:43.350 --> 00:45.150
...He lost himself.

00:45.420 --> 00:48.020
That doesn't follow.
Optimus knew Megatron... !

00:48.100 --> 00:49.200
They were like BFFs!

00:51.840 --> 00:54.840
If Optimus did not know his own name,

00:55.040 --> 00:58.740
perhaps it is because the title of Prime
hasn't yet been granted to him.

00:59.480 --> 01:00.310
- Huh?
- What?

01:00.560 --> 01:01.260
Say again?

01:01.540 --> 01:04.739
With the power of the Matrix no longer within him,

01:05.090 --> 01:10.090
it would stand to reason that Optimus
has reverted to his pre-Prime state:

01:10.320 --> 01:14.220
the historical archivist, Orion Pax.

01:14.300 --> 01:16.000
You mean, in his mind.

01:16.100 --> 01:18.600
Are you telling me Prime thinks
he is some kind of

01:18.640 --> 01:20.640
librarian?
AND a Decepticon?!

01:23.280 --> 01:24.380
Attention, crew.

01:24.760 --> 01:28.660
Our guest is currently in isolation,
to help ease his transition.

01:29.680 --> 01:30.680
But when Orion Pax emerges,

01:31.930 --> 01:34.330
he is to be shown every courtesy.

01:34.380 --> 01:38.980
And the first to address him as "Optimus Prime"
will have their voice-box torn out.

01:39.130 --> 01:40.330
Lord Megatron.

01:40.570 --> 01:44.570
Is it wise, to allow an Autobot,
current or former,

01:44.570 --> 01:46.270
full run of the premises?

01:46.820 --> 01:49.620
Nothing happens aboard this ship
without my knowledge.

01:49.770 --> 01:53.170
You would do well to remember that, Airachnid.

01:53.290 --> 01:55.390
But there's no need for concern.

01:55.550 --> 02:00.050
Orion does not possess the same fight
Optimus is so renown for.

02:00.050 --> 02:02.450
Then what use is he to our Cause?

02:02.680 --> 02:07.680
Ah, rest assured, Orion Pax
will indeed earn his stripes.

